<body style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:250%">
  <div><img src="/source/change/img/adp1.png" style="width:100%"></div>
<div style="width:90%;margin:0 auto">
  <p style="margin-left:5%;width:90%">消费金额：</p>
  <input class="form-control pagename" placeholder="请输入金额" id="inputm" onkeyup="value=value.replace(/[^\d{1,}\.\d{1,}|\d{1,}]/g,'')">€
  <hr><br>
  <p style="margin-left:5%;width:90%">退税金额：</p>
  <input class="form-control pagename" disabled="disabled" id="outm">€
  <hr><br>
  <p style="margin-left:5%;width:90%">在店铺购物金额至少175欧元，科当天在同一店铺申请退税服务。</p>

  <p style="margin-left:5%;width:90%">退税服务仅适用于游客。更多详细信息请<br><a href="#">点击这里</a></p>
</div>
  <div><img src="/source/change/img/adp2.png" style="width:100%"></div>
  <script type="text/javascript">
    $(function(){
      $("#inputm").change(function(){
        var m = $("#inputm").val();
        var a = m * 0.2;
        $("#outm").val(a);
      })
    });
  </script>
</body>
